{"id":465,"category_slug":"english-conversations","category_name":"Conversations","position":67,"title":"67. We Must be Out of Them","subtitle":"","level":"A2","parts":14,"url":"https://dailydictation.com/exercises/english-conversations/67-we-must-be-out-of-them.465/listen-and-type","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/67-we-must-be-out-of-them-2022-03-07-21-27-01/0-67-we-must-be-out-of-them.mp3","transcript":"Hi! Sorry I'm late. I missed the bus.\nOh, that's OK. I had time to clean up before you came.\nYou don't look very good.\nI must be getting a cold. I've been sneezing all day.\nA-A-ATCHOO!\nBless you.\nThank you.\nYou must be getting a cold.\nWhy don't you go lie down? I'll bring you some aspirin.\nI don't see any aspirin in the medicine cabinet.\nWe must be out of them.\nI'll go to the drugstore. Is there anything else we need?\nCould you get some... ATCHOO...\nI don't know if they sell ATCHOO here, but I'll check!","youtube_video_id":"","details_cached_at":"2026-06-15T20:48:56","challenges":[{"position":1,"content":"Hi! Sorry I'm late. I missed the bus.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/67-we-must-be-out-of-them-2022-03-07-21-27-01/1.mp3","time_start":2.9,"time_end":5.42},{"position":2,"content":"Oh, that's OK. I had time to clean up before you came.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/67-we-must-be-out-of-them-2022-03-07-21-27-01/2.mp3","time_start":5.42,"time_end":8.37},{"position":3,"content":"You don't look very good.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/67-we-must-be-out-of-them-2022-03-07-21-27-01/3.mp3","time_start":8.44,"time_end":9.83},{"position":4,"content":"I must be getting a cold. I've been sneezing all day.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/67-we-must-be-out-of-them-2022-03-07-21-27-01/4.mp3","time_start":9.83,"time_end":13.28},{"position":5,"content":"A-A-ATCHOO!","audio_url